high_descs: Turn around, then left to find the stove.
Pick up the pot from the back left burner.
Carry the pot and turn right to locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the pot inside. Shut the door then open it. Take out the pot and shut the door.
Hold the pot and turn to the left.
Place the pot on the counter, to the right side.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Make a left to walk to the stove.
Pick up a black pot from the stove.
Turn around and cross the kitchen to the fridge,
Put the pot in the fridge, let it chill, and take it back out.
Make left and walk towards the kitchen counter to the right of the sink.
Set the black pot down on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a black pot in the fridge to put it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the stove top.
Pick up the large pot from the stove top.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator on the left.
Put the pot in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the counter which is to the right of the sink.
Put the pot on the counter, in front of and to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pot on a counter top.
